    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been treated with real love? This car is in wonderful shape and drives like a dream! It\u2019s been my trusty companion, and while it shows a little bit of character from the road, it\u2019s still looking sharp and ready for its next big adventure. It's the perfect choice if you want a quality vehicle that's ready to hit the road today. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
