    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Up for sale is an exceptional driver\u2019s E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 inline-six featuring Double VANOS and individual throttle bodies. This unit delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission for total engagement. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the suspension utilizes refreshed bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. It features a mechanical M-Variable limited-slip differential, providing predictable torque distribution under load. Mechanically robust with a documented history of rod bearing and VANOS maintenance, this car presents in honest condition with minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use. It remains a visceral, analog masterpiece for the discerning pilot.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Routine maintenance documented. Minor exterior wear. Interior is intact. Mechanically sound.",
