    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is the ideal choice for a buyer seeking a blend of luxury and proven reliability. The exterior paint still holds a brilliant luster, though a few minor stone chips on the lower front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel well are present upon close inspection\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept in a smoke-free environment. The leather seats show light, natural creasing but remain firm and free of any punctures or thinning. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the adaptive cruise control, is fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; the engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and I have maintained a comprehensive log of all oil changes and scheduled services. The tires are at roughly 70% tread, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car has been garage-kept and meticulously cared for, offering a premium driving experience for its next owner.",
