      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline, with a recently serviced dual-VANOS system ensuring optimal cam timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise shift throws, sending power to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates to address known structural fatigue, paired with refreshed bushings for sharpened turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with enthusiastic use, the mechanical vitals remain robust, making this an ideal candidate for those who prioritize analog feedback and track-ready engineering.",
